    • asyncManagePing

      public java.lang.Thread asyncManagePing()
      This method creates a thread used to check if the connection is still alive between client and server. Every 7 seconds the thread wakes up and check if while it was sleeping another ping was received. If no ping was received it means that the connection was lost, and proceed to end the game.
      Returns:
      The actual thread
